raw 27 new "session-interrupt-recovery — local/remote divergence 방지"
  slug session-interrupt-recovery
  enforce tool/checkpoint_recovery.hexa
  decl self/session/last_synced.json
  scope user interrupt → local commit orphaned → push fail → local/remote divergence. 2-phase commit 필요: git add/commit → checkpoint write → push. 중단 지점 어디서든 recover 가능해야 함.
  why ufo.txt L264-310 pattern — interrupt 후 local 은 commit 있고 remote 는 없는 상태. 재개 시 push 시도 → diverged. checkpoint atomic write 로 last_synced 기록 → 다음 session 에서 재개 가능. raw:self-host-fixpoint(raw#18) + raw:proof-carrying(raw#10) + raw:silent-error(raw#12) 확장.
  note raw#8 + raw#10 + raw#19 확장 — session lifecycle 가 SSOT 복구 경로
  follow-up session checkpoint atomic write — interrupt-safe (tmp + rename)
  follow-up push-verify stage — local HEAD == remote HEAD 확인 후 last_synced 갱신
  proof tool/checkpoint_recovery.hexa

